hadiths[21]{hadithnumber,text}:
2690,"(Qubaa ke) banu-Amr-bin-Auf mein aapas mein kuchh takraar ho gaee thi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne kai ashaab ko sath lekar unke yahan unmein suleh karaaney ke liye gaey aur Namaz ka waqt ho gaya, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif na la sakey. chunanche Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne aagey badh kar azan di, abhi tak chunkey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif nahi laey they isliye wo (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ki hidayat ke mutaabiq) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur unse kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahin ruk gaey hain aur Namaz ka waqt ho gaya hai, kya aap logon ko Namaz padha dengey ? unhon-ne kaha ke haan, agar tum chaaho. iske baad Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Namaz ki takbeer kahi aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aagey badhey (namaz ke darmyaan) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safon ke darmyan se guzartey huey pehli saf mein aa pahunchey. log baar-baar hath par hath maarney lagey. magar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz mein kisi dusri taraf mutwajjeh nahi hotey they ( magar jab baar-baar aisa hua to (aap mutwajjeh huey aur malum kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aap ke peechhey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath ke ishaarey se unhein hukm diya ke jis tarah wo Namaz padha rahe hain, usey jari rakhein. lekin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna hath utha kar Allah ki hamd bayan ki aur ultey paon peechhey aagey aur saf mein mil gaey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey badhey aur Namaz padhai. Namaz se farigh ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur unhein hidayat ki ke logo! jab Namaz mein koi baat pesh aati hai to tum hath par hath maarney lagtey ho. hath par hath maarna aurton ke liye hai (mardon ko) jiski Namaz mein koi baat pesh aaey to usey Subhan-Allah kehna chahiye, kyonke ye lafz jo bhi suney ga wo mutwajjeh ho jaeyga aey abu-Bakar! jab maine ishara bhi kar diya tha to phir aap logon ko Namaz kyon nahi padhatey rahe? unhon-ne arz kya, abu-Qahaafa ke betey ke liye ye baat munasib na thi ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hotey huey Namaz padhaaey."
2691,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya gaya, agar aap Abdullah-bin-Ubai ( munafiq (ke yahan tashrif ley chaltey to behtar tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske yahan aik gadhey par Sawar ho kar tashrif ley gaey. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) paidal Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. jidhar se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) guzar rahe they wo keechad wali zameen thi. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske yahan pahunchey to wo kehney laga zara aap door hi rahiye aap ke gadhey ki boo ne mera dimagh pareshan kar diya hai. is par aik Ansari sahabi boley ke Allah ki qasam! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka gadhaa tujh se zyada khushbu daar hai. Abdullah ( munafiq ( ki taraf se uski qaum ka aik shakhs us sahabi ki is baat par ghussa ho gaya aur donon ne aik doosrey ko bura bhala kaha, phir donon taraf se donon ke himaayatii mushta'il ho gaey aur haathaa-paaii, chhadi aur jootey tak naubat pahunch gaee. hamein malum hua hai ke ye aayat isi mauqe par nazil hui thii. ( وإن طائفتان من المؤمنين اقتتلوا فأصلحوا بينهما‏ ( ''agar musalmanon ke 2 giroh aapas mein lad padein to unmein suleh kara do.''"
2692,aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna tha ke jhoota wo nahi hai jo logon mein aapasii suleh karaaney ki koshish karey aur uske liye kisi achi baat ki chughlii khaaey ya usi silsile ki aur koi achi baat keh de.
2693,"Quba ke logon ne aapas mein jhagdaa kya aur naubat yahan tak pahunchi ke aik ne doosrey par patthar phainkey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab uski itlaa di gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''chalo ham unmein suleh karaaengey.''"
2694,"( Allah Taala ke us farmaan وإن امرأة خافت من بعلها نشوزا أو إعراضا‏ ''agar koi aurat apne shauhar ki taraf se be-tawajjohii dekhey.'' ki tafseer mein farmaayaa:ki us se murad aisa shauhar hai jo apni biwi mein aisi cheezein paaey jo usey pasand na hon, umr ki zyadti wghaira aur isliye usey apne se juda karna chahta ho aur aurat kahey ke mujhey juda na karo (nafqa wghaira) jis tarah tum chaho detey rehna, to unhon-ne farmaya ke agar donon is par razi ho jayen to koi harj nahi hai."
2695,"aik dehati aaya aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! hamarey darmyan kitabullah se faisla kar dijiye. doosrey fareeq ne bhi yahi kaha ke usne sach kaha hai. aap hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kar dein. dehati ne kaha ke mera ladka iske yahan mazdoor tha. phir us ne uski biwi se zina kya. qaum ne kaha tumharey ladkey ko rajm (sangsaar) kya jaeyga lekin maine apne ladkey ke us jurm ke badley mein so bakriyan aur aik baandi de di, phir maine ilm walon se puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke iske siwa koi sura nahi ke tumharey ladkey ko so kode lagaey jayen aur aik saal ke liye mulk badr kar diya jaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main tumhara faisla kitabullah hi se karunga. baandi aur bakriyan to tumhen wapas lota di jati hain, albatta tumharey ladkey ko so kode lagaey jaeinge aur aik saal ke liye mulk badr kya jaeyga aur Anees tum (ye qabila Aslam ke sahabi they) us aurat ke ghar jao aur usey rajm (sangsaar) kar do (agar wo zina ka iqrar kar ley) chunanche Anees gaey, aur (choonke usne bhi zina ka iqrar kar liya tha us liye) usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diyaa.''"
2696,"eik dehati aaya aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! hamarey darmyan kitabullah se faisla kar dijiye. doosrey fareeq ne bhi yahi kaha ke usne sach kaha hai. aap hamara faisla kitabullah ke mutabiq kar dein. dehati ne kaha ke mera ladka iske yahan mazdoor tha. phir us ne uski biwi se zina kya. qaum ne kaha tumharey ladkey ko rajm (sangsaar) kya jaeyga lekin maine apne ladkey ke us jurm ke badley mein so bakriyan aur aik baandi de di, phir maine ilm walon se puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke iske siwa koi sura nahi ke tumharey ladkey ko so kode lagaey jayen aur aik saal ke liye mulk badr kar diya jaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main tumhara faisla kitabullah hi se karunga. baandi aur bakriyan to tumhen wapas lota di jati hain, albatta tumharey ladkey ko so kode lagaey jaeinge aur aik saal ke liye mulk badr kya jaeyga aur Anees tum (ye qabila Aslam ke sahabi they) us aurat ke ghar jao aur usey rajm (sangsaar) kar do (agar wo zina ka iqrar kar ley) chunanche Anees gaey, aur (choonke usne bhi zina ka iqrar kar liya tha us liye) usey rajm (sangsaar) kar diyaa.''"
2697,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne hamarey Deen mein az khud koi aisi cheez nikaalii jo usmein nahi thi to wo radd hai. uski riwayat Abdullaah-bin-Ja'far makhramii aur abdul-Waahid-bin-Abii Aun ne Sa'd-bin-Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) se ki hai.
2698,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hudaibiya ki suleh (Quraish se) ki to uski dastaawez Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne likhi thi. unhon-ne usmein likha Muhammad Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se. mushrekeen ne is par aetraz kya ke lafz Muhammad ke sath Rasulullah na likho, agar aap Rasulullah hotey to ham aap se ladtey hi kyon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya Rasulullah ka lafz mitaa do, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine kaha ke main to usey nahi mitaa sakta, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud apne hath se wo lafz mitaa diya aur mushrekeen ke sath us shart par suleh ki ke aap apne ashaab ke sath (aainda saal) teen din ke liye Makka aaein aur hathiyar miyan mein rakh kar dakhil hun. shagirdon ne puchha ke جلبان السلاح ( jiska yahan zikr hai) kya cheez hoti hai? to unhon-ne bataya ke miyan aur jo cheez iske andar hoti hai (uska naam جلبان  hai)."
2699,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zi-Qada ke mahiney mein Umre ka ehram baandhaa. lekin Makka walon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Shahar mein dakhil nahi honey diya. aakhir suleh is par hui ke) aainda saal (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein teen roz qiyam karengey. jab suleh naamaa likha janey laga to usmein likha gaya ke ye wo suleh naamaa hai jo Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya hai. lekin mushrekeen ne kaha ke ham to usey nahi mantey . agar hamein ilm ho jaey ke aap Allah ke rasool hain to ham aapko na rokein. bas aap sirf Muhammad-bin-Abdullah hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Rasulullah bhi hun aur Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bhi hun. iske baad aap ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke Rasulullah ka lafz mitaa do, unhon-ne arz kya nahi Allah ki qasam! main to ye lafz kabhi na mitaaoonga. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud dastaawez li aur likha ke ye uski dastaawez hai ke Muhammad-bin-Abdullah ne us shart par suleh ki hai ke Makka mein wo hathiyar miyan mein rakhey baghair dakhil na hongey. agar Makka ka koi shakhs unke sath jana chaahega to wo usey sath na ley jaengey. lekin agar unke ashaab mein se koi shakhs Makka mein rehna chaahega to usey wo na rokengey. jab (aainda saal) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka tashrif le gaey aur (Makka mein qiyam ki) muddat poori ho gaee to Quraish Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kaha ke apne sahib se kahey ke muddat poori ho gaee hai aur ab wo hamarey yahan se chaley jaaein. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka se rawaana honey lagey. us waqt Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik bachchii chachaa-chachaa karti aaein. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein apne sath ley liya, phir Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke paas hath pakad kar laey aur farmaya, apni chacha-zad behan ko bhi sath le lo, unhon-ne usko apne sath sawar kar liya. phir Ali, Zaid aur Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ka jhagdaa hua. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke iska main zyada mustahiq hon, ye mere chacha ki bachchii hai. Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ye mere bhi chacha ki bachchii hai aur uski khala mere nikah mein bhi hain. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke mere bhai ki bachchii hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bachchii ki khala ke haq mein faisla kya aur farmaya ke khala maa ki jagah hoti hai. phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke tum mujh se ho aur main tum se hun. Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke tum sura aur aadaat w akhlaq sab mein mere jaise ho. Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke tum hamarey bhai bhi ho aur hamarey maula bhii."
2700,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suleh Hudaibiya mushrekeen ke sath teen sharaait par ki thi, (1) ye ke mushrekeen mein se agar koi aadmi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aa jaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey wapas kar dengey. lekin agar musalmanon mein se koi mushrekeen ke yahan panah lega to ye log aisey shakhs ko wapas nahi karengey. (2) ye ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aainda saal Makka aa sakengey aur sirf teen din thahrengey. (3) ye ke hathiyaar, talwaar, teer wghaira niyaam aur tarkash mein daal kar hi Makka mein dakhil hongey. chunanche Abu-Jandal (Raziallahu anhu) (jo musalman ho gaey they aur Quraish ne unko qaid kar rakha tha) bediyon ko ghaseet'tey huey aaey, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein (sharaait muaahida ke mutaabiq) mushrikon ko wapas kar diya. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Muammal ne Sufiyan se abu-Jandal ka zikr nahi kya hai aur) إلا بجلبان السلاح (ke bajaey ( إلا بجلب السلاح‏) ke alfaz naql kiye hain."
2701,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Umre ka ehram baandh kar nikley, to kuffaare-Quraish ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Baitullah janey se rok diya. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qurbani ka janwar Hudaibiya mein zabah kar diya aur sar bhi wahin mundwaa liya aur kuffaare-Makka se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us shart par suleh ki thi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aainda saal Umra kar sakengey. talwaaron ke siwa aur koi hathiyar sath na laaengey. (aur wo bhi niyaam mein hongi) aur Quraish jitney din chaahengey us se zyada Makka mein na thahar sakengey. (yani teen din) chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aainda saal Umra kya aur sharaait ke mutabiq Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka mein dakhil huey, phir jab teen din guzar chukey to Quraish ne Makka se chaley janey ke liye kaha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se wapas chaley aaey."
2702,Abdullah-bin Sehal aur Mahiisa-bin-Mas'ood-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) khaibar gaey. khaibar ke yahudiyon se musalmanon ki un dinon suleh thi.
2703,"nazar ki beti Rabe (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik ladki ke daant tod diye. is par ladki walon ne taawaan maanga aur un logon ne maafi chaahii, lekin maaf karne se unhon-ne inkar kya. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badla leney ka hukm diya. (yani unka bhi daant tod diya jaey) Anas-bin-Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! Rabe ka daant kis tarah todaa ja sakega. nahi us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath maboos farmaya hai, iska daant nahi todaa jaeyga Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Anas! kitabullah ka faisla to badla leney ( qisaas ( hi ka hai. chunanche ye log razi ho gaey aur maaf kar diya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke kuchh bandey aisey bhi hain ke agar wo Allah ki qism kha lein to Allah Taala khud unki qism poori karta hai. fazari ne (apni riwayat mein) Humaid se, aur unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ye zyadti naql ki hai ke wo log razi ho gaey aur taawaan ley liya."
2704,"qism Allah ki jab Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) (Muaawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke muqaabley mein) pahadon mein lashkar lekar pahunchey, to Amr-bin-al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha (jo ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke musheere-khaas they) ke main aisa lashkar dekh raha hun jo apne muqabil ko neest w naabood kiye baghair wapas na jaeyga Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha aur qism Allah ki, wo un donon ashaab mein zyada achchhey they, ke aey Amr! agar us lashkar ne us lashkar ko qatl kar diya, ya us ne usko qatl kar diya, to (Allah taala ki bargah mein) logon ke maamlon (ki jawab dehii ke liye) mere sath kon zimme-dari lega, logon ki bewa aurton ki khabar-geeri ke silsiley mein mere sath kon zimmedaar hoga. logon ki aal-aulaad ke silsiley mein mere sath kon zimme-daar hoga. aakhir Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan Quraish ki shaakh banu-abd-shams ke 2 aadmi bhejey. Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Samraa aur Abdullaah-bin-Aamir-bin-kurez, aap ne un donon se farmaya ke Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan jao aur unke samney suleh pesh karo, unse is par guftgu karo aur faisla unhiin ki marzii par chhod do. chunanche ye log aaey aur aap se guftgu ki aur faisla aap hi ki marzii par chhod diya. Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya, ham banu-abdul-Muttalib ki aulad hain aur ham ko khilafat ki wjah se rupya-paisaa kharch karne ki aadat ho gaee hai aur hamarey sath ye log hain, ye khoon kharaaba karne mein taaq hain, baghair rupya diye manney waley nahi. wo kehney lagey ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) aapko itnaa-itnaa rupya dene par razi hain aur aap se suleh chahtey hain. faisla aap ki marzii par chhoda hai aur aap se puchha hai. Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke uski zimme-dari kon lega? un donon qaasidon ne kaha ke ham iske zimme-daar hain. Hasan ne jis cheez ke mutaalliq bhi poochha, to unhon-ne yahi kaha ke ham iske zimme-daar hain. aakhir aap ne suleh kar li, phir farmaya ke maine Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha, wo bayan kartey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko member par ye farmatey suna hai aur Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pahlu mein they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kabhi logon ki taraf mutwajjeh hotey aur kabhi Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf aur farmatey ke mera ye betaa sardaar hai aur shayad iske zariey Allah Taala musalmanon ke 2 azeem girohon mein suleh karaaeyga. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha mujh se Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne bayan kya ke hamarey nazdeek us hadis se Hasan Basri ka Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se sunnaa Sabit hua hai."
2705,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne darwazey par 2 jhagdaa karne walon ki awaz suni jo buland ho gaee thi. waqia ye tha ke aik aadmi doosrey se qarz mein kuchh kami karne aur taqazey mein kuchh narmii baratney ke liye keh raha tha aur doosra kehta tha ke Allah ki qasam! main ye nahi karunga. aakhir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas gaey aur farmaya ke is baat par Allah ki qism khaney waley sahib kahan hain? ke wo aik achchha kaam nahi karengey. un sahabi ne arz kya, main hi hon ya Rasulullah! ab mera bhai jo chahta hai wahi mujh ko bhi pasand hai."
2706,"Abdullah-bin hadrad Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) par unka qarz tha, unse mulaqat hui to unhon-ne unka peechhaa kya, (aakhir takraar mein) donon ki awaz buland ho gaee. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) idhar se guzrey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Kab! aur apne hath se ishara kya, jaisey aap keh rahe hon ke aadha (qarz kam kar de) chunanche unhon-ne aadha qarz chhod diya aur aadha liya."
2707,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''insaan ke badan ke (teen so sath jodon mein se) har jod par har us din ka sadqa wajib hai jis mein suraj tuloo hota hai aur logon ke darmyan insaf karna bhi aik sadqa hai.''
2708,"unmein aur aik Ansari sahabi mein jo badr ki ladai mein bhi Sharik they, Madina ki pathreelii zameen ki nali ke barey mein jhagdaa hua. wo apna muqaddima Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley gaey. donon hazraat us naley se (apne baagh) sairaab kya kartey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Zubair! tum pahley sairaab kar lo, phir apne padosi ko bhi sairaab karne do, is par Ansari ko ghussa aa gaya aur kaha, ya Rasulullah! us wjah se ke ye aap ki phoophii ke ladkey hain. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey ka rang badal gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Zubair! tum sairaab karo aur pani ko (apne baagh mein) itni der tak aaney 2 ke diwar tak chadh jaey. us martaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko unka pura haq ata farmaya, us se pahley Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa faisla kya tha, jis mein Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) aur Ansari sahabi donon ki ri'aayat thi. lekin jab Ansari ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ghussa dilaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko qanoon ke mutabiq pura haq ata farmaya, Urwa ne bayan kya ke Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, qism Allah ki! mera khayal hai ke ye aayat فلا وربك لا يؤمنون حتى يحكموك فيما شجر بينهم‏ isii waqia par nazil hui thi ''to hargiz nahin! terey rab ki qasam, ye log us waqt tak momin na hongey jab tak apne aapas ke ikhtilaf mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke faisley ko dil w jaan se taslim na kar lein''."
2709,"mere walid jab Shahid huey to un par qarz tha. maine unke qarz-khaahon ke samney ye sura rakhi ke qarz ke badley mein wo (is saal ki khajoor ke) phal ley lein. unhon-ne us se inkar kya, kyonke unka khayal tha ke us se qarz pura nahi ho sakega, main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab phal tod kar marbad (wo jagah jahan khajoor khushk kartey they) mein jama kar do (to mujhey khabar 2) chunanche maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey. sath mein Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan khajoor ke dher par baithey aur is mein barkat ki dua farmai, phir farmaya ke ab apne qarz-khaahon ko bula la aur unka qarz ada kar de, chunanche koi shakhs aisa baqi na raha jiska mere bap par qarz raha aur maine usey ada na kar diya ho. phir bhi 13 wasq khajoor baqi bach gaee. saat (7) wasq ajwa mein se aur chh wasq lon mein se, ya chh wasq ajwa mein se aur saat (7) wasq lon mein se, baad mein main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maghrib ke waqt ja kar mila aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hansey aur farmaya, Abu-Bakar aur umr ke yahan ja kar unhein bhi ye waqia bata do. chunanche maine unhein batlaayaa, to unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jo karna tha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo kya. hamein jabhi malum ho gaya tha ke aisa hi hoga. Hisham ne Wahab se aur unhon-ne Jaabir se Asr ke waqt (Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki haziri ka ( zikr kya hai aur unhon-ne na Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr kya aur na hansney ka, ye bhi bayan kya ke (Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha) mere walid apne uper tees wasq qarz chhod gaey they aur ibne-Ishaq ne Wahab se aur unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se Zohar ki Namaz ka zikr kya hai."
2710,"unhon-ne ibne-abii-Hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) se apna qarz talab kya, jo unke zimma tha. ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak ka waqia hai. masjid ke andar un donon ki awaz itni buland ho gaee ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi suni. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt apne hujrey mein tashrif rakhtey they. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar aaey aur apne hujre ka parda utha kar Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko awaz di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pukara aey Kab! unhon-ne kaha ya rasoolullaah, main hazir hun. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath ke ishaarey se farmaya ke aadha maaf kar de. Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine kar diya ya Rasulullah! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (ibne-abii-Hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) se) farmaya ke ab utho aur qarz ada kar do."
